parameters: \coIt's a shame we couldn't stop that assassin
from killing our prisoner. Still, I greatly
appreciate the help from you four.
\coWelcome to the Solus Valley Jail... thrilling, isn't it?
\coWelcome to the Solus Valley Jail... \}hopefully I don't get knocked out again...
\ctYou have to let me out, I'm begging you! I can't
spend another second with these losers!
\ssThis guy won't stop whining! I can't take it anymore!
these four are on a mission grander than we
can comprehend. If there's any chance we
can learn something, we have to take it!
\chiefRight wh- ah, yes! Welcome to the Solus Valley Jail, my friends!
can you show us to his cell?
\coI really advise against it... but your word
is law, chief. Let's pay him a visit.
\coSo, they're attempting a prison break? Not on our watch!
\coI tried... I really tried my best...
